Description: GTK CAN / CAN FD bus monitor using SocketCAN
 PCAN-View Linux is a GTK3 desktop application for monitoring, transmitting,
 and recording CAN and CAN FD traffic via the Linux SocketCAN subsystem
 (PF_CAN). It is inspired by PEAK-System PCAN-View.
 .
 Features:
  * Live statistics bar (interface, bitrate, bus load, Rx/Tx/Err, bus state).
  * Real-time receive trace with timestamp, ID, type, DLC and data.
  * One-shot and cyclic transmission; CAN FD payloads up to 64 bytes.
  * Trace capture with CSV export.
  * Listen-only mode and configurable nominal / data bit rates.
 .
 Distributed by Taksys.
